{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":833,"text":"By the year 2050, the population\nof Africa will have doubled."},{"time":5406,"text":"One in four people on Earth\nwill be African at that point,"},{"time":8810,"text":"and this is both really exciting\nand daunting all at once."},{"time":12519,"text":"It's really exciting because,\nfor the first time in the modern era,"},{"time":15687,"text":"there will be enough Africans on the Earth\nto bully everybody else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18894,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20108,"text":"I'm only kidding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22105,"text":"But it's daunting, because we're going\nto have to have economies"},{"time":25131,"text":"that can sustain this population growth,"},{"time":27093,"text":"and many of the people\nare going to be very young."},{"time":29621,"text":"Now most of governments in Africa\nhave a plan for this economic growth --"},{"time":33315,"text":"in Kenya, we call ours Vision2030 --"},{"time":35947,"text":"and they're all predicated\non industrialization."},{"time":39327,"text":"The thing is, though, that the world"},{"time":41126,"text":"is going through the Fourth\nIndustrial Revolution right now,"},{"time":43992,"text":"which means that there's a merger"},{"time":45589,"text":"of the physical, cyber,\nand biological worlds."},{"time":47788,"text":"It means that because of\nmassive interconnectivity"},{"time":51574,"text":"and the availability\nof artificial intelligence and robotics,"},{"time":55115,"text":"many of the jobs that we know\nand are used to right now"},{"time":57712,"text":"won't exist in the future."},{"time":59187,"text":"So the challenge\nis a lot greater, in many ways,"},{"time":61449,"text":"than it even was when Asia\nwas industrializing, for example."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65390,"text":"To add to this, one of the kinds\nof person that you need"},{"time":69692,"text":"for industrialization is an engineer,"},{"time":71867,"text":"and they're really in short supply\non the continent."},{"time":74343,"text":"If you compare, for example,\nthe number of engineers"},{"time":76864,"text":"that those same Asian countries had"},{"time":78646,"text":"a couple of decades ago\nwhen they were industrializing,"},{"time":81318,"text":"we fall far short."},{"time":84289,"text":"And I've taught for a while,"},{"time":85679,"text":"and many of the students\nwho are studying engineering"},{"time":88201,"text":"end up actually working\nin auditing firms and banks,"},{"time":91500,"text":"and many of them spend half their time\ndoing accounting and so on"},{"time":94580,"text":"as they're preparing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96538,"text":"Now, I was fortunate enough\nto do my undergrad and postgrad education"},{"time":100849,"text":"in the UK and the US,\nin countries, environments,"},{"time":103412,"text":"where there was all the equipment\nthat you required,"},{"time":106118,"text":"all the sophistication in the systems,"},{"time":108245,"text":"and then I worked\nfor about three years in Japan"},{"time":110563,"text":"doing R&amp;D for a large firm."},{"time":112523,"text":"And so I was very used\nto having good equipment,"},{"time":114809,"text":"and went back home"},{"time":115997,"text":"and joined the Faculty of Engineering\nat the University of Nairobi,"},{"time":119199,"text":"wanting to contribute\nand be on the continent."},{"time":121379,"text":"And I quickly found\nI was really quite useless,"},{"time":123887,"text":"because there wasn't all the equipment\nthat I had become accustomed to available."},{"time":128572,"text":"And I was teaching students who I would\nfind very bright ideas in their minds"},{"time":132620,"text":"and they'd be presenting\nthings that I knew"},{"time":134645,"text":"if only we had sufficient equipment,"},{"time":136446,"text":"they'd be able to really contribute\nto the challenge of industrialization."},{"time":141708,"text":"So I kind of had to change hats,\nand became quite entrepreneurial"},{"time":145701,"text":"and started looking for money\nto buy the equipment that we required."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149201,"text":"And I heard about a concept\nout of MIT, called the Fab Labs."},{"time":153072,"text":"These are digital fabrication labs"},{"time":155099,"text":"that allow, in a rather small space\nwith not very expensive equipment,"},{"time":158711,"text":"people to have access to these tools"},{"time":160850,"text":"to be able to make almost anything,"},{"time":163002,"text":"as the slogan goes."},{"time":164728,"text":"And so I was able to convince\na government official"},{"time":167454,"text":"to buy one of these for the university\nwhere I was teaching."},{"time":170312,"text":"And immediately, we had wonderful results."},{"time":172336,"text":"We saw all kinds\nof innovations coming through,"},{"time":174653,"text":"and for the first time\nin this context at the university,"},{"time":177487,"text":"engineering students\nfrom different disciplines"},{"time":181122,"text":"were doing the lab and practical exercises\ntogether in the same space."},{"time":185049,"text":"Normally, they'd be siloed."},{"time":186924,"text":"And not just that, but students\nwho weren't engineers at all"},{"time":189824,"text":"were also working in the same place,"},{"time":191750,"text":"and non-students, people\nwho had nothing to do with the university,"},{"time":194957,"text":"were also coming into this space."},{"time":196584,"text":"So you had this rich mix of people,"},{"time":198275,"text":"people who think\ndifferently from one another,"},{"time":200444,"text":"and this always\nis really good for innovation."},{"time":202853,"text":"I was really proud of what we were seeing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204965,"text":"So you can imagine my surprise"},{"time":206433,"text":"when one day the dean of engineering\ncame and said to me,"},{"time":209471,"text":"\"Kamau, the students\nwho spend most of the time in the Fab Lab"},{"time":213392,"text":"are failing their exams.\""},{"time":215251,"text":"I said, \"What do you mean?\""},{"time":217791,"text":"And I looked into it, and he was right,"},{"time":220203,"text":"and the reason they were failing"},{"time":221790,"text":"is that they'd honed their skills\nso well in certain things"},{"time":224605,"text":"that they were going out into the city\nand offering services for money."},{"time":228081,"text":"So they were making money --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229522,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":230597,"text":"and they therefore\nweren't focusing on their studies."},{"time":233352,"text":"And I thought,\nwhat a good problem to have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235433,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":236473,"text":"Don't quote me on that.\nI'm an academician."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239613,"text":"So we needed to scale this,"},{"time":242241,"text":"and at the university,\nthings were a bit too bureaucratic,"},{"time":245447,"text":"and so I moved out and I hooked up\nwith people who, in Nairobi,"},{"time":248686,"text":"were providing spaces for IT experts"},{"time":251360,"text":"to share fast internet\nand things like that."},{"time":254067,"text":"And some of these places\nare really quite famous."},{"time":256414,"text":"They've made Kenya famous for IT."},{"time":259774,"text":"And together we set up a space\nwhich we are setting up right now."},{"time":264306,"text":"We've moved from where we were."},{"time":265919,"text":"We are in a much larger space,"},{"time":267463,"text":"and we're sort of making available\na wide range of equipment,"},{"time":270991,"text":"including the digital fabrication\ntools that I mentioned,"},{"time":273848,"text":"and analog tools,"},{"time":275349,"text":"to anybody really, on a membership basis."},{"time":277889,"text":"It's a bit like a gym,\nso you come in, you pay,"},{"time":280168,"text":"you get taught how to use the equipment,"},{"time":282106,"text":"and then you're set free to innovate\nand do whatever it is that you want,"},{"time":285845,"text":"and you don't have to be\nan engineer, necessarily."},{"time":288498,"text":"And some of the people in the space\nare setting up a small company."},{"time":291713,"text":"They just need a space at a desk,"},{"time":293407,"text":"and so we provide that at a fee,"},{"time":295004,"text":"and others take up bigger spaces\nand are able to set up their offices."},{"time":298314,"text":"They're further along."},{"time":299570,"text":"Maybe their company has been running\nfor a certain period of time."},{"time":302690,"text":"And so we're able\nto accommodate all of this"},{"time":304783,"text":"in an innovation space\nthat is really quite active."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308966,"text":"What you're seeing in this image\nover here is Douglas,"},{"time":311785,"text":"and Douglas is an electrical engineer,"},{"time":313705,"text":"one of the people\nwho was really active in the Fab Lab."},{"time":316379,"text":"I'm pretty sure he passed his exams."},{"time":318221,"text":"And the image on the top left\nis a copper sheet."},{"time":321857,"text":"And he designed a circuit\nthat the client came to him and said,"},{"time":324866,"text":"\"I need this circuit\nfor a pay-as-you-go system.\""},{"time":327954,"text":"And so this is a model for business"},{"time":330365,"text":"that's made accessibility to goods\nand services for very poor people"},{"time":335190,"text":"really much easier,\nbecause they're able to pay a little bit,"},{"time":338127,"text":"like a dollar a day, for example,"},{"time":339946,"text":"for a specific service."},{"time":341618,"text":"And so this company wanted\nto pilot a new idea that they had,"},{"time":344627,"text":"and so they just needed 50 circuits,"},{"time":346436,"text":"so they hired him to make them,"},{"time":347938,"text":"and what you're seeing him doing there is,"},{"time":350041,"text":"he's able to design on the computer\nwhat the circuit will be"},{"time":353381,"text":"and then transfer it\nto an etching process --"},{"time":355509,"text":"that's the image on the top right --"},{"time":357249,"text":"and then populate the board\nusing this robot."},{"time":360517,"text":"And so what would normally take him maybe\na day or something to solder by hand,"},{"time":365232,"text":"he can do in a few minutes\nusing this machine."},{"time":367455,"text":"So he was able to complete\nthe entire order within Gearbox,"},{"time":370272,"text":"and this is really important,"},{"time":371716,"text":"because if it wasn't for\nwhat we provided right now,"},{"time":374503,"text":"he would have had to have hired\na company in China to do this,"},{"time":378410,"text":"and because it's such a small order,\nit would have taken a long time."},{"time":381694,"text":"It would be a small company,"},{"time":383234,"text":"because big companies\nwouldn't take small orders,"},{"time":385583,"text":"and even then, if they got a bigger order,"},{"time":387608,"text":"they'd bump him off in favor of that."},{"time":389766,"text":"And there's language problems and so on,"},{"time":391696,"text":"so being able to do it in country\nis really very important,"},{"time":394497,"text":"and of course piloting as a phase\nwithin the progress of the business idea"},{"time":399895,"text":"is extremely important, because you can\ngo back and make corrections and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404836,"text":"In this image -- Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406633,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":408483,"text":"In this image you see on the top left,"},{"time":410318,"text":"what you're looking at is a 3D render\nof a digital fabrication machine."},{"time":413677,"text":"In this instance,\nit doubles as a plasma cutter"},{"time":416619,"text":"and also a wood router."},{"time":418350,"text":"And so the plasma cutter makes possible\nthe cutting of plate and sheet metal,"},{"time":423358,"text":"and basically, you make\na design on the computer"},{"time":425627,"text":"and send it over to the machine,"},{"time":427207,"text":"and then quickly and precisely,\nit will cut the shapes you want."},{"time":430287,"text":"But in this machine,"},{"time":431468,"text":"you can also change the plasma cutter\nand put on a spindle,"},{"time":435177,"text":"and then you can carve wood as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437367,"text":"So this was designed\nby my Head of Engineering."},{"time":439995,"text":"His name is Wachira,"},{"time":441487,"text":"and when I hired him about two years ago,"},{"time":444215,"text":"I asked him, \"Just give me two years,"},{"time":446123,"text":"and by the time you've trained\na lot of people"},{"time":448329,"text":"so that we have good staff under you,"},{"time":450378,"text":"then you can move out\nand become a good story for us.\""},{"time":452954,"text":"And that's exactly what's just happened."},{"time":454926,"text":"He's got two types of customers."},{"time":457220,"text":"The higher-tier customer"},{"time":459848,"text":"is a company that's actually\nusing his machine"},{"time":462443,"text":"to cut sheet metal\nfor Isuzu truck fabrication in Nairobi,"},{"time":466301,"text":"which is being done by General Motors."},{"time":468372,"text":"So we're really proud to be able to say"},{"time":470277,"text":"that we have an original\nequipment manufacturer in Nairobi"},{"time":473635,"text":"that's provided what's effectively\nan industrial robot"},{"time":476406,"text":"to supply parts for General Motors."},{"time":479451,"text":"Now this is really important --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":480993,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":483774,"text":"and it's really important because\nthe population growth being what it is,"},{"time":487996,"text":"a lot of very large companies\nare looking very closely"},{"time":490719,"text":"at the market that's developing in Africa."},{"time":492809,"text":"So in Kenya right now, we have\nVolkswagen, Peugeot, Renault,"},{"time":495658,"text":"we have Mercedes doing lorries,"},{"time":497227,"text":"and we've also got Toyota,\nthey've been there a long time."},{"time":499994,"text":"And these are all manufacturers\nplanning to assemble vehicles"},{"time":502877,"text":"and in the future,\nto manufacture in the country."},{"time":505203,"text":"Many of them are planning\nto train lots of people that they'd hire,"},{"time":508371,"text":"and that's really important\nfor the economy,"},{"time":510444,"text":"but when the magic really happens,"},{"time":512101,"text":"when these companies begin to buy\ntheir parts for the vehicles"},{"time":516126,"text":"from local companies,"},{"time":517441,"text":"so supply chain development\nis something that's very important"},{"time":520401,"text":"for us to be able to pivot\nand to have very productive economies,"},{"time":523608,"text":"and that's something\nwe're focused on at our space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526799,"text":"This other image shows\nanother class of customer that he has."},{"time":530602,"text":"On the top left,"},{"time":531777,"text":"you have these people\nwho are actually using very crude tools"},{"time":534745,"text":"to work metal and wood."},{"time":536652,"text":"And Kenya has a population\nof about 44 million people."},{"time":540792,"text":"The work force is about 13 million,"},{"time":542832,"text":"and about 80 to 90 percent of those\nare in the informal sector."},{"time":546420,"text":"And what you're seeing in the image\nat the top left over there"},{"time":549381,"text":"is very typical of semi-skilled artisans"},{"time":553048,"text":"who are making products\nfor the marketplace"},{"time":555636,"text":"that are really crude."},{"time":556823,"text":"Their production rate is very slow."},{"time":558748,"text":"The quality of the product isn't high."},{"time":561013,"text":"And so we've teamed\nWachira up with a bank,"},{"time":564061,"text":"and the bank is paying him\nto train people from this sector"},{"time":567203,"text":"on how to use this industrial robot."},{"time":570131,"text":"And the result is that some of them"},{"time":572624,"text":"are going to be able to get loans\nto buy the machine for themselves."},{"time":576609,"text":"Others will be able to go to centers\nwhere they can carry their material,"},{"time":580132,"text":"get the design done,"},{"time":581427,"text":"and take the materials back\nthat have been made really, really fast"},{"time":584951,"text":"and assemble them in their own spaces."},{"time":586833,"text":"So somebody making a gate,\nfor example, out of metal,"},{"time":589642,"text":"may take a week to make just one gate,"},{"time":591602,"text":"but with this machine,\nthey might make 10 in a day."},{"time":594079,"text":"So the productivity of a large swathe\nof our population"},{"time":596775,"text":"should be able to jump by a quantum\namount, quite significantly,"},{"time":601677,"text":"because of this kind of machine."},{"time":603256,"text":"And that's what we're at the beginning of,\nso this is really very exciting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607350,"text":"This is another person who uses our space."},{"time":609415,"text":"Her name is Esther."},{"time":610590,"text":"She's in her mid-20s,"},{"time":611765,"text":"and she came in very passionate\nabout a problem that she explained."},{"time":614961,"text":"She said that schools days are missed\nevery month by young girls"},{"time":618367,"text":"because of their menstrual cycle,"},{"time":619986,"text":"and they're not able\nto buy a sanitary towel."},{"time":622523,"text":"And the reason that she described"},{"time":624579,"text":"was that the manufacturers\npackaged these in bundles of seven to 10,"},{"time":628571,"text":"and breaking it down\nis unhygienic at the retail level,"},{"time":632056,"text":"and packaging each one\nof them is too expensive."},{"time":634762,"text":"So she thought up an idea,\nwhich is brilliant, and simple."},{"time":637961,"text":"Why don't we just use vending machines?"},{"time":639844,"text":"And she, in a very clean environment,\ncan break down the bundles"},{"time":643059,"text":"and fill up the vending machines,"},{"time":644956,"text":"and then girls can buy\nthese sanitary towels"},{"time":648005,"text":"in the privacy of a toilet,\nin a public space, in a school, and so on."},{"time":652195,"text":"She was able to pilot this\nand it worked really very well,"},{"time":655172,"text":"and she's been able to sort of\nget the bugs out and so on."},{"time":657912,"text":"So the significance here\nis that the piloting process is possible."},{"time":661397,"text":"She's not an engineer."},{"time":662654,"text":"She was able to engage people in our space\nto be able to help her to do this,"},{"time":666311,"text":"and she's off and running now\nwith a business accelerator,"},{"time":669063,"text":"so we expect to see great results."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670728,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":673829,"text":"In this image you're looking at --"},{"time":675837,"text":"the result of a master's project\nthat was done at University of Nairobi"},{"time":679805,"text":"by Tony Nyagah, an engineering student,"},{"time":681755,"text":"and he just integrated\na solar cell into a roof tile"},{"time":684886,"text":"and decided to make it a business."},{"time":686593,"text":"He joined up with his sister\nwho is an architect,"},{"time":688915,"text":"and they have this business,"},{"time":690286,"text":"and they present the roof tile to a person\nwho is doing development and say,"},{"time":693976,"text":"\"You can buy it for the cost\nof just the roof tile without the solar.\""},{"time":697575,"text":"So they're giving it at a discount,"},{"time":699421,"text":"and then they'll build them\nusing the internet of things over time,"},{"time":703049,"text":"they'll pay about a third\nof the utility charges for the electricity"},{"time":707243,"text":"and they can sell the excess\nback to the grid."},{"time":710220,"text":"And so they'll make their money over time,"},{"time":712506,"text":"and they've been able to do\nquite a few installments."},{"time":715783,"text":"We were very proud to be able\nto show this to somebody kind of famous,"},{"time":719863,"text":"as you can see there,"},{"time":721538,"text":"and this other famous guy\nactually presented the same idea,"},{"time":724523,"text":"but as far as we're concerned,\nif it was after us, so --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":727168,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":728236,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":732538,"text":"So in closing, going forward,\nof course being able to prototype"},{"time":736784,"text":"and do low manufacturing\nin this kind of a setting"},{"time":739180,"text":"is very important\nfor the industrialization process,"},{"time":741728,"text":"but we're also taking advantage\nof a lot of new ways of doing things:"},{"time":744991,"text":"the open source movement,"},{"time":746271,"text":"distributive manufacturing,\ncircular production."},{"time":748587,"text":"So it's all very important\nfor not just industrializing"},{"time":751950,"text":"and being able to meet people's needs,"},{"time":753785,"text":"but also making sure\nthat the environment is taken care of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756730,"text":"We're also really interested in culture."},{"time":758905,"text":"We have lots of discussions in our space\naround who we were as Africans,"},{"time":762311,"text":"who we are today, and who we want to be"},{"time":764247,"text":"vis-à-vis things like consumerism\nand ethnicity and corruption and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768745,"text":"So we see ourselves as providing,\nadding value to people"},{"time":772588,"text":"by teaching them to add value\nto things or materials"},{"time":776215,"text":"so that they can build things that matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778390,"text":"Thank you very much for your attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780273,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":783208,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784383,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}